(4, 151, 'admin', 'nmc2010@gmail.com', '', '192.168.1.54', '2017-06-28 02:22:16', '2017-06-28 02:22:16', 'But then I tried a drink with chia seeds and it reminded me of bubble tea! Albeit with tiny bubbles. In a flash decades of green sprouty images disappeared, replaced with food possibilities.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
