(6, 151, 'admin', 'nmc2010@gmail.com', '', '192.168.1.54', '2017-06-28 02:22:33', '2017-06-28 02:22:33', 'At the table, each person gets to mix the ingredients together in his or her bowl. Don’t expect to hear too much conversation as the first few bites go down!s', 0, '1', '', '', 4, 0),
