(8, 364, 'admin', 'nmc2010@gmail.com', '', '192.168.1.54', '2017-06-28 02:21:29', '2017-06-28 02:21:29', 'All you have to do is purée some blueberries in almond milk and then stir in chia seeds. For extra zing a little cinnamon and honey. Let it soak overnight or for at least a couple of hours. Then top with whole blueberries and some toasted almonds to eat.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(9, 364, 'admin', 'nmc2010@gmail.com', '', '192.168.1.54', '2017-06-28 02:21:38', '2017-06-28 02:21:38', 'All you have to do is purée some blueberries in almond milk and then stir in chia seeds. For extra zing a little cinnamon and honey. Let it soak overnight or for at least a couple of hours. Then top with whole blueberries and some toasted almonds to eat.', 0, '1', '', '', 8, 0),
