to/chasm</a></b> \n\nDappled light over the Colorado River and Grand Canyon in Arizona, USA. From a trip a few years ago with <a href=\"https://www.davemorrowphotography.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dave Morrow</a> when we explored the South East of the States.\n\nAlso, I have released (and still have a few) tickets for our <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com/faroe-islands-april-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Faroe Islands photography workshop</a> in April, 2018.\n\nI\'m just back from shooting in Canada for Alberta Tourism, so feel free to <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">check out my Instagram</a> for some images from Jasper National Park.\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b>No images in comments please.</b>\n\n<b>Details</b>\n<i>Nikon D800 / ISO 50 / f/5.6 / 1/500s / AF-S Nikkor 28-300mm f/3.5-5.6G ED VR @ 56mm / Location: Grand Canyon, United States</i>\";s:5:\"m_url\";s:63:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/4455/37988098906_3369cf3a1c_m.jpg\";s:5:\"t_url\";s:63:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/4455/37988098906_3369cf3a1c_s.jpg\";s:5:\"l_url\";s:61:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/4455/37988098906_3369cf3a1c.jpg\";s:9:\"photo_xml\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";s:10:\"1509377317\";s:10:\"date_taken\";s:25:\"2015-01-27T19:59:29-08:00\";s:15:\"date_taken_nice\";s:18:\"January 27th, 2015\";s:4:\"guid\";s:18:\"/photo/37988098906\";s:11:\"author_name\";s:8:\"TheFella\";s:10:\"author_url\";s:39:\"https://www.flickr.com/people/thefella/\";s:11:\"author_nsid\";s:12:\"11224136@N07\";s:11:\"author_icon\";s:87:\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4239/buddyicons/11224136@N07.jpg?1498182937#11224136@N07\";s:9:\"photo_url\";s:63:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/4455/37988098906_3369cf3a1c_b.jpg\";s:9:\"thumb_url\";s:63:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/4455/37988098906_3369cf3a1c_s.jpg\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"682\";s:5:\"width\";s:4:\"1024\";s:7:\"l_width\";s:3:\"500\";s:4:\"tags\";s:484:\"rock rim northamerica us photoshop coloradoriver coloradoriverbasin unitedstatesofamerica dslr thefel