om/photos/thefella/20166324354/\";s:11:\"description\";s:1733:\"			<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/people/thefella/\">TheFella</a> posted a photo:</p>\n	\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/thefella/20166324354/\" title=\"Valley View\"><img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/5649/20166324354_fea69c77c5_m.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"160\" alt=\"Valley View\" /></a></p>\n\n<p><b><a href=\"http://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"http://f8.pe\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Photo Expeditions</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a></b><br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/valley-view\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/valley-view</a></b> <br />\n<br />\nThis is El Capitan catching the morning light beyond the Merced River in Yosemite National Park during an amazing photography adventure around The States with <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/daves-f-stop/\">Dave Morrow</a> earlier this year.<br />\n<br />\nSorry for my lack of activity, but I\'ve been super busy with some travelling and <a href=\"https://instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> work. I\'m not long back from a shoot in the Faroe Islands for the tourist board. Some photos on my Instagram and hopefully some good ones to come on Flickr once I get around to processing them!<br />\n<br />\nLater this year I should be doing a shoot in Japan for RT Holidays, so if you live here, let me know and maybe we can go shooting together.<br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>No images in comments please.</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>Details</b><br />\n<i>Nikon D800 / ISO 50 / f/11 / 30s / Nikkor 14-24mm f/2.8G ED @ 14mm / Location: Yosemite, United States</i></p>\";s:15:\"description_raw\";s:1318:\"<b><a href=\"http://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"http://f8.pe\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Photo Expeditions</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a></b>\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/valley-view\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/valley-view</a></b> \n\nThis is El Capitan catching the morning light beyond the Merced River in Yosemite National Park during an amazing photography adventure around The States with <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/daves-f-stop/\">Dave Morrow</a> earlier this year.\n\nSorry for my lack of activity, but I\'ve been super busy with some travelling and <a href=\"https://instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> work. I\'m not long back from a shoot in the Faroe Islands for the tourist board. Some photos on my Instagram and hopefully some good ones to come on Flickr once I get around to processing them!\n\nLater this year I should be doing a shoot in Japan for RT Holidays, so if you live here, let me know and maybe we can go shooting together.\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b>No images in comments please.</b>\n\n<b>Details</b>\n<i>Nikon D800 / ISO 50 / f/11 / 30s / Nikkor 14-24mm f/2.8G ED @ 14mm / Location: Yosemite, United States</i>\";s:5:\"m_url\";s:63:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/5649/20166324354_fea69c77c5_m.jpg\";s:5:\"t_url\";s:63:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/5649/20166324354_fea69c77c5_s.jpg\";s:5:\"l_url\";s:61:\"https://live.staticflickr.com/5649/20166324354_fea69c77c5.jpg\";s:9:\"photo_xml\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";s:10:\"1440256492\";s:10:\"date_taken\";s:25:\"2015-02-06T15:36:43-08:00\";s:15:\"date_taken_nice\";s:18:\"February 6th, 2015\";s:4:\"guid\";s:18:\"/photo/20166324354\";s:11:\"author_name\";s:8:\"TheFella\";s:10:\"author_url\";s:39:\"https://www.flickr.com/people/thefella/\";s:11:\"author_nsid\";s:12:\"11224136@N07\";s:11:\"author_icon\";s:87:\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4239/buddyicons/11224136@N07.jpg?1498182937#11224136@N07\";s